A SocketBackend for PowerDNS. Features UNIX Socket, TCP and UDP connectors. Uses JSON for discussions between the other end and itself.

TBD: Query formats

Configuration

The only configuration option available will be

socket-connection-string=connstr

connstr := connector:options
options := option,option,option
option := key=value

Common options

timeout = seconds

Connector 'unix'

path = /path/to/socket

Connector 'tcp'

host = hostname or address
port = port
reuse = reuse same tcp connection

Connector 'udp'

host = hostname or address
port = port
